Release 0.2.0 - 20-June-2004
* Startup/Shutdown support
  - Added socket shutdown listener/handler
  - Unix init script
  - Windows batch file configure JavaService

* Build changes
  - Release archives expand into a directory with the version in the name
  - Checks so up to date tasks don't run
  - Tasks for install
  - RPM packages for source and binary

* Server changes
  - SSL support
  - Cache property files in method Server.getProperties()
  - Configuration locations can be passed on the command line
  - Honor load-on-startup for servlets
  - Allow multiple listeners (e.g. HTTP, HTTPS) to share a ServletContext
  - Notify listeners of life cycle events

Release 0.1 - 09-June-2004
* Initial relase
